description: Patriarch Irinej, 90, tested positive after attending a large funeral for Montenegro's top cleric.
title: Covid-19: Serbian Orthodox Patriarch Irinej dies
title_page: Covid-19: Serbian Orthodox Patriarch Irinej dies - BBC News
maintext: Thousands of mourners had gathered at the event without masks or maintaining social distancing. Many of those present kissed the bishop's body as it lay in an open casket. Bishop Amfilohije had himself defied Covid regulations on public gatherings in Montenegro.
